	* w32.c (init_winsock): Dynamically load new server and UDP
	socket functions.
	(socket_to_fd): New function.
	(sys_socket): Use it.
	(sys_setsockopt, sys_listen, sys_getsockname, sys_accept) 
	(sys_recvfrom, sys_sendto): New wrapper functions.

